{"tid":1395513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你知唔知香港有一班人，每個禮拜一都會合法罷工？","createTime":"2019-08-01T18:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T20:54:34.000Z","uid":296674,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8fb327734cc83b114dcef05dbde0ef619a8a64","tid":1395513,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:42:55.000Z","msg":"...冇錯，就係一班教牧同工（即係喺教會，或者教會附屬機構返工嘅人）<br />\n因為佢哋<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">禮拜日要搞崇拜，所以變相星期日返工，星期一補假</span></strong></span>㗎。<br />\n<br />\n你仲唔快啲嗌埋佢哋8。5去集會？<br />\n香港咁細，教會梗有一間喺左近，佢哋都算出咗好多力保護我哋呢一班發緊夢嘅人，你唔係唔同佢哋一齊去Sing Hallelujah 呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n利申：而家喺外國留學，我阿媽禮拜一會合法罷工"},{"pid":"917525b7bb6cb1e3961754b18220a19658ed610d","tid":1395513,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:05:57.000Z","msg":"8月5號 三罷，人不在心在，到時見"},{"pid":"11a5ec8cb89808504ce31386d7db794a0c5ea636","tid":1395513,"uid":289560,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:07:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73b5b7c48d7d378c7910dcfee351b595bb5954af","tid":1395513,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:10:13.000Z","msg":"你以為我阿媽好想罷工咩 係教會逼佢嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bd9e6eadaffe4c2e2bf038f58c7d9d8fb8b669","tid":1395513,"uid":211122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11a5ec8cb89808504ce31386d7db794a0c5ea636","tid":1395513,"uid":289560,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:07:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:21:12.000Z","msg":"收皮啦食屎狗5毛！<br />\n你唔死對香港真係百害無一利！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk